// Orphen fast-forward patch set (strict letterbox == 0x01)
// Base profile: Profile C (x8 cadence), corrected and stable.
//
// Notes:
// - Addresses use 2xxxxxxx format for PCSX2 pnach.
// - Strict check uses DAT_00355054 == 0x01 to avoid false triggers when 0xFFFFFFFF appears.
// - "Hard renderer off" is optional and disabled by default (uncomment to test).

