// ------------------------------------------------------------
// Optional: hard disable main renderer while fast-forward path is active
// ------------------------------------------------------------
// Effect:
// - During the cutscene fast-forward gated path, skip render calls unconditionally.
// - This can remove flicker, but may hide scene visuals/subtitle layers depending on draw order.
//
// Enable by uncommenting this line:
// patch=1,EE,20223F84,extended,1000000C
